title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Airbus H135 helicopter
description:
The Airbus H135 is the first helicopter which is available for MSFS 2020. It is still under development but the developers have been so friendly to make it available for free. In this video we will look at the current state of the helicopter and fly around with it a bit near the airport.

The latest version of the helicopter can be downloaded from flightsim.to:
https://flightsim.to/file/8970/airbus-h135-helicopter-project
